@node iswdigit
@section @code{iswdigit}---decimal digit wide character test
@findex iswdigit
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <wctype.h>
int iswdigit(wint_t @var{c});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
@code{iswdigit} is a function which classifies wide-character values that
are decimal digits.

@*
@strong{Returns}@*
@code{iswdigit} returns non-zero if @var{c} is a decimal digit wide character.

@*
@strong{Portability}@*
@code{iswdigit} is C99.

No supporting OS subroutines are required.

@*
